      <title>加拿大保守派的避税计划是多伦多股票的潜在福音</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/canada-conservatives-tax-shelter-plan-is-potential-boon-for-toronto-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党的选举承诺将允许个人避免对国内公司的某些投资所得税受到称赞，这在多伦多的金融区受到称赞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/canada-conservatives-tax-shelter-plan-is-potential-boon-for-toronto-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 17:17:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国国家银行Bpifrance推出了2700万美元的加密基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/french-state-bank-bpifrance-launches-27-million-crypto-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国投资银行Bpifrance表示，它将推出2500万欧元（2700万美元）的加密货币策略，直接投资于数字资产，这是对新生部门的更广泛的支持策略的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/french-state-bank-bpifrance-launches-27-million-crypto-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
